### Organizer Registration & Auth API - REST Client Format
### Base URL
@BASE_URL = http://localhost:3000
@organizerToken = 

### 1. Register New Organizer
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "neworganizer@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123",
  "confirmPassword": "SecurePass123",
  "name": "Event Company Ltd",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "contactPerson": "John Doe",
  "address": "123 Main Street, City",
  "website": "https://example.com",
  "description": "Professional event organizer",
  "logo": "https://example.com/logo.png"
}

### 2. Login
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "contact@techevents.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get Profile Only
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 4. Get All Events (Separate API)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/events
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 5. Get Active Events Only
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/events?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 6. Get Upcoming Events Only
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/events?status=upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 7. Get Past Events Only
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/events?status=past
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 8. Get Events with Limit and Sort
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/events?limit=5&sort=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}

### 9. Update Profile
PATCH {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "address": "New Address",
  "website": "https://newwebsite.com"
}

### 10. Change Password
PATCH {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newPassword123",
  "confirmPassword": "newPassword123"
}

### 11. Logout
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/organizers/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
